Metadata-Version: 2.0
Name: nice-oom-daemon
Version: 0.0.1
Summary:   A daemon for docker which sends signals to containers when they hit their memory soft limit.
  
Home-page: https://github.com/mmontagna/nice-oom-daemon
Author: Marco Montagna
